      "span_text": "TDI recordings were analyzed for strain in the subendocardial, midmyocardial and subepicardial layers of the inferior LV wall using high resolution-zoomed parasternal short-axis recordings (at the level of papillary muscles) (Figure 1 ), using our highly reproducible method reported in healthy subjects [CITATION_1] ."
